OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few bright
OL,6,Fspells and isolated showers at first.
OL,7,FOtherwise, cloudy with patchy rain in
OL,8,Fthe evening, clearing east overnight.
OL,9,FFurther cloud and rain will reach the
OL,10,Fsouthwest by morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FBreezy and mostly cloudy
OL,13,Fthroughout the day as outbreaks of
OL,14,Frain move east, these heavy at times.
OL,15,FStaying driest and brightest towards
OL,16,FEast Lothian and Berwickshire.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
