OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FLargely dry with bright or sunny
OL,7,Fspells on Monday morning, a few
OL,8,Fshowers in the afternoon. Bright or
OL,9,Fsunny spells and scattered showers
OL,10,FTuesday and Wednesday, some heavy and
OL,11,Fthundery.
